{"tid":881492,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"到香港旅遊不用為語言發愁了，請大膽講普通話吧！","createTime":"2018-10-29T13:05:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-29T15:40:26.000Z","uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d72b57b9ecf6ffa7d32d6e4f17d362a9a9dc4c64","tid":881492,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T13:05:00.000Z","msg":"無意中睇到呢個大陸人寫香港游記，自稱專材移民到香港住o左十鳩幾年。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以在大陸無樣真，連旅行blog都要寫假野，好可憐。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bbs.qyer.com/post.php?action=jump&amp;pid=16968621\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbbs.qyer.com%2Fpost.php%3Faction%3Djump%26pid%3D16968621&d=TH25f6O4l%2BkW713sTJIbZtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=dd02ade3\" target=\"_blank\">http://bbs.qyer.com/post.php?action=jump&amp;pid=16968621</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n奔向香港，你準備好了嗎？<br />\n<br />\n請在香港大膽講普通話！<br />\n我雖然在廣東生活多年，但由於平時與同事交流都用普通話，所以直到現在也依然只能聽，不能講，可是這並不妨礙我在香港的生活。<br />\n<br />\n即便有部分香港人不能講普通話，但這些年耳濡目染，他們聽懂是沒問題的。在港島地區，香港人都以會講普通話為榮。<br />\n<br />\n近十年，大陸迅速崛起，香港發起了&ldquo;優才引進計劃&rdquo;，吸引了不少大陸人才到香港工作，我老公就是其中之一。十年過去，他已經成為香港永久居民，我也成了香港媳婦。<br />\n<br />\n值得一提的是，在老公的公司，能講普通話的都是牛人，而且香港員工特別希望能講一口流利的普通話，經常把我老公當成免費的陪練。<br />\n<br />\n到香港旅遊不用為語言發愁了，請大膽講普通話吧！"},{"pid":"ed09f20a00972802b3cb963da084484e46fc0eed","tid":881492,"uid":5995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T13:06:09.000Z","msg":"佢岩呀"},{"pid":"9a1cca134728fdd7ae0e9b5557904ed426fa6239","tid":881492,"uid":216127,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T13:06:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b3c206a360df3a88e366a9eb5bd29b18ec734906","tid":881492,"uid":54777,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T13:07:09.000Z","msg":"在港島地區，香港人都以會講普通話為榮。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9b3cd5c32493dc71ed98a7ae04d95cff29b7f1c","tid":881492,"uid":121580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T13:10:51.000Z","msg":"一聽到普通話問路<br />\n我就會汪汪汪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4a383a6b29f5b86232f8194b6ef666185dae9cc","tid":881492,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T13:23:04.000Z","msg":"鱔稿<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"806176df4e931f81dd96705b91aaa56ee0dae6dc","tid":881492,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3c206a360df3a88e366a9eb5bd29b18ec734906","tid":881492,"uid":54777,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T13:07:09.000Z","msg":"在港島地區，香港人都以會講普通話為榮。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T14:21:06.000Z","msg":"一定用廣東話答"},{"pid":"f8a8fc4aeaf697db7801c869df326cce2bb3b349","tid":881492,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T14:26:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你自己講普通話唔緊要<br />\n關鍵係唔好大聲同冇禮貌<br />\n叫人大聲擺明伏9人"},{"pid":"e72c186bc2261c9db045fabe7ce4f4fae5e525bf","tid":881492,"uid":76009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T14:28:57.000Z","msg":"其實一向都係唔理你講英文法文俄文，都係講普通話嫁啦!"},{"pid":"1e0a0dce3e6d4661718957f3c46bf1694e546ff6","tid":881492,"uid":90660,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T15:40:26.000Z","msg":"牛人?cow man?大陸狗做牛做馬先諗撚到呢啲濕鳩詞語"}]}